<div class="container">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col s12">
			<div class="post-new-container">
				<form>
					<div class="row">
						<div class="col s12">
							<div class="col s12">
								<h4>新增房屋</h4>
								<br>
							</div>
						</div>
				    <div class="col s12">
				      <ul class="tabs">
				        <li class="tab col s2"><a class="active" href="#basic">基礎資訊</a></li>
				        <li class="tab col s2"><a href="#space">空間及價格</a></li>
				        <li class="tab col s2"><a href="#description">描述</a></li>
				        <li class="tab col s2"><a href="#amenity">家具及設施</a></li>
				        <li class="tab col s2"><a href="#photo">圖片</a></li>
				        <li class="tab col s2"><a href="#date_status">預約及開放</a></li>
				      </ul>
				    </div>

				    <div id="basic" class="col s12">

							<div class="col m6 s12">
								<div class="col s12">
									<p class="form-title">房屋類型</p>
									<div class="hr"></div>
							    <span style="margin-right: 8px;">
							      <input class="with-gap" name="group1" type="radio" id="test2"  />
							      <label for="test2">整層住家</label>
							    </span>
							    <span style="margin-right: 8px;">
							      <input class="with-gap" name="group1" type="radio" id="test3"  />
							      <label for="test3">分租套雅房</label>
							    </span>
							  </div>
							  <div class="col s12">
								  <p class="form-title">您的房子在哪些學校附近呢？</p>
								  <div class="hr"></div>
							  </div>
							    <p class="col m6 s12">
							      <input type="checkbox" class="filled-in" id="filled-in-box1" />
							      <label for="filled-in-box1">政治大學</label>
							    </p>
							    <p class="col m6 s12">
							      <input type="checkbox" class="filled-in" id="filled-in-box2" />
							      <label for="filled-in-box2">台灣大學</label>
							    </p>
							    <p class="col m6 s12">
							      <input type="checkbox" class="filled-in" id="filled-in-box3" />
							      <label for="filled-in-box3">世新大學</label>
							    </p>
							    <p class="col m6 s12">
							      <input type="checkbox" class="filled-in" id="filled-in-box4" />
							      <label for="filled-in-box4">台北教育大學</label>
							    </p>
							    <p class="col m6 s12">
							      <input type="checkbox" class="filled-in" id="filled-in-box5" />
							      <label for="filled-in-box5">台科大</label>
							    </p>
							    <p class="col m6 s12">
							      <input type="checkbox" class="filled-in" id="filled-in-box6" />
							      <label for="filled-in-box6">台師大</label>
							    </p>
							    <p class="col m6 s12">
							      <input type="checkbox" class="filled-in" id="filled-in-box7" />
							      <label for="filled-in-box7">北醫大學</label>
							    </p>


						  </div>
							<div class="col m6 s12">
								<div class="col s12">
									<p class="form-title">你歡迎外國租客嗎？</p>
									<div class="hr"></div>
								  <div class="switch">
								    <label>
								      不需要
								      <input type="checkbox">
								      <span class="lever"></span>
								      很樂意
								    </label>
								  </div>
								  <blockquote>承租給外國人可以做國民外交，幫助他們在陌生的土地更容易融入，並有機會獲得更好的報酬。</blockquote>
									<p class="form-title">是否需要英語協助？</p>
									<div class="hr"></div>
								  <div class="switch">
								    <label>
								      不需要
								      <input type="checkbox">
								      <span class="lever"></span>
								      需要
								    </label>
								  </div>
							  </div>
							  <div class="col s12">
								  <p class="form-title">房屋地址</p>
								  <div class="hr"></div>
							  </div>
							  <div class="col m6 s12">
								  <select class="browser-default">
								    <option value="" disabled selected>縣市</option>
								    <option value="1">Option 1</option>
								    <option value="2">Option 2</option>
								    <option value="3">Option 3</option>
								  </select>
							  </div>
							  <div class="col m6 s12">
								  <select class="browser-default">
								    <option value="" disabled selected>鄉鎮市區</option>
								    <option value="1">Option 1</option>
								    <option value="2">Option 2</option>
								    <option value="3">Option 3</option>
								  </select>
							  </div>
				        <div class="input-field col s12">
				          <input id="first_name" type="text" class="validate">
				          <label for="first_name">郵遞區號</label>
				        </div>
				        <div class="input-field col s12">
				          <input id="last_name" type="text" class="validate">
				          <label for="last_name">地址</label>
				        </div>
								<div class="col s12">
									<p class="form-title">是否隱藏地址</p>
									<div class="hr"></div>
								  <div class="switch">
								    <label>
								      不隱藏
								      <input type="checkbox">
								      <span class="lever"></span>
								      隱藏
								    </label>
								  </div>
							  </div>
						  </div>
						  <div class="col s12">
								<div class="text-center" style="margin-top: 48px;">
									<button class="btn-large">下一步</button>
								</div>
						  </div>
				    </div>

				    <div id="space" class="col s12"></div>

				    <div id="description" class="col s12"></div>

				    <div id="amenity" class="col s12"></div>

				    <div id="photo" class="col s12"></div>

				    <div id="date_status" class="col s12"></div>

					</div>
				</form>

			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
